release_note: We re excited to introduce the latest update to Mood Tracker designed to make your health tracking experience more intuitive informative and personalized. Enhanced Reminder System: Set reminders for all your built in measurements including PRN as needed reminders. Tailor each reminder with specific start and end dates for better management. Revamped Goals Screen: We ve simplified the Goals screen to focus solely on your current care plan making it easier to track and achieve your health objectives. Medical Library Expansion: Dive into our newly added Medical Library within Health Pathways. Gain quick and insightful knowledge about your medications and health conditions. Unlimited Measurements for Free: Enjoy the freedom to add unlimited measurements without any cost. This includes the highly requested Refill reminders ensuring you never miss a medication dose. We re committed to enhancing your health tracking experience with Mood Tracker. Update now and explore these new features designed to support your wellness journey!

Immerse in Uninterrupted Soundscapes! Your favorite soundscapes now continue to play even when you switch apps or your screen is off. Perfect for focus or relaxation! Unlock Your Past Activities Easily access your checked in items from the past by tapping on Logs and selecting Show Past Tracked . Never forget a moment! Elevate Your Experience with UI UX Updates Dark mode just got better along with a streamlined More menu engaging journal prompts and refreshed icons. Feel the difference! Experience these new features now. Download the latest version to enhance your daily routine!

In our latest update we ve enhanced the experience with insights from Cognitive Behavioral Therapy CBT principles making it simpler and more engaging to understand your emotions: View Mood Insights in Charts: Uncover new layers of self awareness with our expanded charts including Mood in pixels mood distribution and your best day. Understanding your emotional landscape has never been so vivid. Introducing Line Charts: We ve converted our mood chart from a bar to a line format. Now tracking your emotional journey is more intuitive and comparing feelings across time is easier. Optional Notes: Since notes aren t always necessary we ve tucked them behind a Add Notes button in the check in. They re there when you need them hidden when you don t. We believe these changes will add a touch of elegance and efficiency to your daily reflections. Update now and explore these new features designed with you in mind.
We ve added additional emotions you can track better charting improved performance and now provide better tracking of your holistic health! Give us a try today!
